Configure OpenVSIX as extension marketplace

Adds extensionsGallery configuration to use Open VSX (open-vsx.org) as the
extension marketplace instead of Microsoft's restricted marketplace. This
enables installing extensions in VSCode web builds. Also adds open-vsx.org
to trusted domains to prevent security warnings.
